cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.DB, cs.SE 

The paper deals with detecting fraudulent accounts on the blockchain, which is a security issue. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also uses supervised learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with data analysis and manipulation, which could place it in cs.DB (Databases) or cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the system, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering).
